---
source: tests/cli/snapshot_helpers.rs
expression: normalized
---
Show the status of a training run

Usage: fastskill optimize status [OPTIONS] <run-dir>

Arguments:
  <run-dir>  Path to the run directory

Options:
      --skills-dir <skills-dir>  Override the skills directory path
      --watch                    Poll and re-render every ~2 seconds
      --global                   Use global skills directory (~/.config/fastskill/skills)
  -v, --verbose                  Enable verbose output
  -h, --help                     Print help
  -V, --version                  Print version

Syntax: optimize status <run-dir> [--watch]
